                     <interp inst="t18010218-74-off402" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-74-off402" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010218-74-cd403" type="crimeDate">14th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-74-off402 t18010218-74-cd403"></join>, twenty-four dressed sheep-skins, value 44s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18010218-74-victim443" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Law
                        <interp inst="t18010218-74-victim443" type="surname" value="Law"></interp>
